Bedtools:
intersect:
-wa, -wb, wo, write a, b, or overlap bases numbers
-c, counts
-v, no overlap
-f 0.5, require the minimum of the overlap fraction, -F, report the reverse fraction
merge:
-d, the distance allowed in intervals when combined, file has to be sorted, sort -k1,1 -k2, 2n file.bed

genomecov
-bga, bedgraph (the forth column is the coverage), require the output is bedgraph

JACCARD STATISTICS (index), calculate jaccard similirity
makewindows
-w window size
-s step size, the size of the overlap between window
